Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.31,0:02:55.53,6-normal,,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,0)\fs80\bord3\blur0\3c&HFFFFFF&\c&H000000&\pos(1827,886)\b1}#3  Sang{\c&H138BC6&} Raja, {\c&H000000&}Terdampar{\c&H000000&}.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:05.04,0:01:06.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jasmine!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:09.65,0:01:10.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jasmine!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:14.67,0:01:17.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ah, sial.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:17.15,0:01:18.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,Siapa yang kau bilang sial?!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:50.11,0:02:51.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Aku ingin memastikan kondisinya.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:52.25,0:02:56.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Aku menerima misi dari keluarga Helstea\Nuntuk mengamankan Mana Beast.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:57.15,0:02:59.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Namun, aku terhadang badai.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:59.78,0:03:02.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku sedang melaksanakan misi dari Guild.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:02.01,0:03:05.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terjadi serangkaian kecelakaan kapal nelayan\Ndi lepas pantai dekat ladang.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:05.41,0:03:10.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku datang untuk menyelidiki penyebabnya,\Ntapi terhadang badai.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:11.04,0:03:13.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalian ini menyedihkan.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:13.45,0:03:17.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bisa-bisanya kalian\Nmenjadi petualang Kelas A sepertiku.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:20.18,0:03:21.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau juga sama saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:24.11,0:03:26.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini perahu yang kunaiki bersama Jasmine.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:26.81,0:03:28.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Begitu, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:28.06,0:03:29.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Semoga dia baik-baik saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:30.18,0:03:31.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:33.12,0:03:35.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita tidak bisa menaikinya kalau begini.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:35.18,0:03:38.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi, bagaimana sekarang, Lucas?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:38.35,0:03:40.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak apa-apa, Elijah.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:40.05,0:03:41.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:41.41,0:03:42.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita memang butuh perahu.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:43.35,0:03:46.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dengan kata lain, Lucas memang benar.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:47.21,0:03:48.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tentu saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:48.09,0:03:51.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau dewasa sekali, Note.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:54.98,0:03:56.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku saja berhasil selamat.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:57.81,0:04:00.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia juga pasti baik-baik saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:09.35,0:04:11.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sylvie, apa kau bisa mendengarku?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:11.18,0:04:13.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya. Ada apa, Papa?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:13.78,0:04:16.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku melakukan sedikit kesalahan.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:16.11,0:04:18.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bisa tolong carikan Jasmine untukku?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:18.15,0:04:20.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tentu saja.\NAku harus pergi ke mana?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:20.81,0:04:22.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ke arah laut.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:22.18,0:04:23.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tempatnya...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:25.98,0:04:28.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Note, jawab aku jika kau dengar.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:28.85,0:04:29.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Note!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:35.75,0:04:37.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini salahku.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:38.55,0:04:40.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini tentang Arachne.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:40.85,0:04:43.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kesimpulannya, kita belum tahu.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:43.61,0:04:47.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Namun, hal serupa terjadi di banyak tempat.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:47.58,0:04:49.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Selain itu juga...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:49.06,0:04:50.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:50.85,0:04:52.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Saat menjalankan misi membasmi\NMana Beast Kelas C,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:52.91,0:04:55.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,malah bertemu dengan Mana Beast Kelas A.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:55.71,0:04:58.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku mendengar banyak cerita seperti itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:58.78,0:05:00.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kesalahan dari pihak Guild?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:00.71,0:05:02.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada kemungkinan.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:02.41,0:05:06.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pihak Guild pun sama kebingungannya\Noleh aliansi tiga negara.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:06.15,0:05:08.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada kemungkinan mereka yang menentang\Naliansi tiga negara
Dialogue: 10,0:05:08.44,0:05:11.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,yang menyebabkan semua ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:11.45,0:05:12.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Walaupun kami tak memiliki buktinya.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:14.78,0:05:19.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sebagai ayah, aku ingin dia berhenti\Nmenjadi petualang.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:19.05,0:05:20.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kurasa Arthur takkan menyerah.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:21.61,0:05:25.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sifat keras kepalanya itu menurun dari Alice.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:26.91,0:05:31.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yang bisa kita lakukan saat ini\Nhanyalah lebih waspada.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:31.58,0:05:35.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Saat menjalankan misi nanti,\Nberhati-hatilah lebih dari biasanya.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:37.25,0:05:40.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jasmine, kutitipkan Arthur padamu.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:42.11,0:05:43.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku mengerti.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:48.41,0:05:49.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,Note!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:49.37,0:05:51.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tuan Muda Lucas!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:51.41,0:05:53.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tolong jawab jika Anda mendengar!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:53.98,0:05:56.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ah, sial.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:57.45,0:06:00.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh, ternyata keluarga Wykes.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:00.05,0:06:00.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:00.67,0:06:05.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kami datang ke tempat ini atas perintah\Nlangsung dari Kerajaan Sapin.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:05.01,0:06:06.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Namun, kami terhadang badai.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:06.18,0:06:07.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hanya kami saja yang...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:09.05,0:06:11.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tuan Muda!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:11.14,0:06:11.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,Badai?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:11.90,0:06:14.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ah, Tuan Muda, semoga Anda selamat.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:14.21,0:06:16.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tuan Muda Lucas!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:16.81,0:06:19.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tuan Muda!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:24.55,0:06:26.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Cincin dimensi.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:26.38,0:06:28.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini kali pertama aku melihatnya langsung.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:28.65,0:06:30.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau pernah berpikir untuk membelinya?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:30.95,0:06:34.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Butuh ribuan keping emas\Nbahkan untuk kelas terendah.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:35.31,0:06:37.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa kau tidak memilikinya?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:37.01,0:06:38.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sayangnya tidak.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:40.80,0:06:42.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalian lakukan sisanya.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:45.45,0:06:48.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa kalian tidak bisa mendirikan tenda?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:48.11,0:06:49.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,Seharusnya kami yang bilang begitu.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:49.93,0:06:51.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sudah, sudah.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:53.93,0:06:55.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau mahir sekali, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:55.81,0:06:57.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Partnerku yang mengajariku.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:57.85,0:06:59.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hei, perutku lapar.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:59.78,0:07:02.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa tidak ada bahan makanan?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:05.61,0:07:08.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sepertinya tidak ada, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:08.11,0:07:11.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pasti membawa bahan makanan\Nadalah tugas bawahannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:11.65,0:07:12.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagaimana denganmu?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:12.71,0:07:15.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Akan habis dalam sehari\Njika dimakan bertiga.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:15.25,0:07:16.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Begitu, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:16.75,0:07:18.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:20.64,0:07:22.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa ini cukup?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:22.43,0:07:26.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hebat sekali, kau bisa melakukan apa pun, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:28.41,0:07:30.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lucas, tolong urus ikannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:31.35,0:07:33.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,Masak dengan baik.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:33.75,0:07:35.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hah? Kenapa harus aku?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:35.91,0:07:39.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Karena kau yang paling ahli dalam sihir api\Ndi antara kita, bukan?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:39.56,0:07:40.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tentu saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:40.85,0:07:42.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,Karena itu kami mengandalkanmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:44.78,0:07:47.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,Cih, apa boleh buat.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:53.35,0:07:55.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tolong sisakan bagian yang bisa dimakan, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:55.81,0:07:56.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku mengerti.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:00.71,0:08:02.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Masak dengan benar.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:02.31,0:08:03.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku mengerti!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:12.51,0:08:16.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lihat, ini adalah bakat dari keluarga Wykes.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:18.65,0:08:21.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Saat kadar airnya berkurang,\Nbaru bisa dimakan.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:21.38,0:08:22.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau tahu banyak hal, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:23.65,0:08:24.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dengarkan aku!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:31.18,0:08:32.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lumayan.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:33.01,0:08:37.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bumbunya biasa saja, penampilannya buruk,\Ntapi masih bisa kumakan.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:37.78,0:08:40.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ikan yang kau bakar terasa enak.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:40.37,0:08:41.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tentu saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:42.95,0:08:46.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Untuk selanjutnya,\Ntolong jangan membuang-buang ikan lagi, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:46.58,0:08:49.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak akan kuberi makan jika kau komentar.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:49.58,0:08:53.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu bisa membuatku kesulitan.\NMaafkan aku, Lucas.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:53.05,0:08:55.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baguslah kalau kau mengerti.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:58.31,0:09:00.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau sengaja membuat Lucas melakukannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:00.78,0:09:03.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lebih efisien jika melakukannya bersama, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:03.45,0:09:04.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau berhasil membuatnya bersemangat.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:25.38,0:09:28.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bisa-bisanya kau makan\Nsambil mengenakan topeng itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:29.15,0:09:30.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hebat, bukan?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:56.11,0:09:58.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kemarin aku mengitari pulau ini
Dialogue: 10,0:09:58.85,0:10:01.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,saat mengumpulkan makanan.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:11.35,0:10:14.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pertama, tidak ada orang lain selain kita.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:15.05,0:10:19.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita menemukan perahu yang dipakai\NElijah dan Lucas ke sini,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:19.75,0:10:21.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,tapi sudah tidak bisa dipakai lagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:22.81,0:10:25.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada dua hal yang bisa kita lakukan.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:25.01,0:10:28.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Menunggu pertolongan\Natau pergi dengan usaha sendiri.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:28.45,0:10:29.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yang bisa diharapkan pertolongan...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:29.91,0:10:32.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jasmine adalah petualang Kelas AA.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:32.91,0:10:35.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia pasti selamat dan bisa menemukanku.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:36.41,0:10:38.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau sangat memercayainya, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:38.31,0:10:39.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lalu bagaimana dengan cara satunya lagi?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:41.51,0:10:43.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita tidak jauh dari benua.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:43.71,0:10:45.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita pasti bisa menyeberang.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:45.45,0:10:47.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dua-duanya bukan pilihan bagus.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:48.25,0:10:51.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa boleh buat, biar kuberi tahu.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:51.38,0:10:53.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Target dari misiku.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:53.81,0:10:57.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Memang skalanya kecil,\Ntapi ia mampu mengendalikan cuaca.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:57.21,0:10:59.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Akan gawat jika bertemu dengannya di laut.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:00.35,0:11:02.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi, penyebab kecelakaan kapal nelayan...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:02.51,0:11:04.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dan yang membuat kapal kita tenggelam...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:04.78,0:11:06.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Memang ulahnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:06.51,0:11:09.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Karena bahayanya Mana Beast ini,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:09.05,0:11:13.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,pihak kerajaan menyerahkan misi ini\Nkepada keluarga Wykes.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:13.41,0:11:14.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa ada informasi lain?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:15.11,0:11:16.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia membuat sarang di dekat perairan
Dialogue: 10,0:11:16.69,0:11:19.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,dan menjadikan daerah sekitarnya\Nsebagai wilayah kekuasaan.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:19.05,0:11:21.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Seharusnya dia ada di suatu tempat\Ndi pulau ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:21.78,0:11:23.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Akan kubakar ia sampai mati.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:24.74,0:11:26.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tunggu, Lucas.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:27.95,0:11:30.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Akan lebih efisien jika kita\Nmelakukannya bertiga, bukan?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:31.41,0:11:32.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan sampai menggangguku.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:39.71,0:11:40.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Arthur.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:41.41,0:11:43.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kyu!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:46.61,0:11:48.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa kau ada di sini?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:00.51,0:12:02.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Arthur masih hidup, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:04.85,0:12:07.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Syukurlah, Arthur.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:10.58,0:12:11.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku harus bergegas.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:17.38,0:12:18.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:18.81,0:12:19.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:19.70,0:12:22.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak salah lagi, ini sarangnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:22.85,0:12:25.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tolong siapkan tembakan\Nyang paling besar, Lucas.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:25.11,0:12:28.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baiklah, biar kutunjukkan kekuatan\Nkeluarga Wykes yang sebenarnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:55.98,0:12:58.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagaimana? Hebat, bukan?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:58.09,0:13:00.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya, lebih dari bayanganku.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:00.45,0:13:02.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tahan dirimu sedikit saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:02.41,0:13:03.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sepertinya aku sudah berlebihan.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:03.95,0:13:06.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kuharap Mana Core-nya tersisa.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:08.81,0:13:09.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:09.85,0:13:11.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Cepat menjauh!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:28.65,0:13:30.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Agak terlalu besar, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:30.41,0:13:32.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya, agak.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:39.81,0:13:41.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Akan kupancing.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:41.21,0:13:42.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tolong siapkan tembakan yang besar, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:43.91,0:13:46.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku mengerti, akan kusiapkan sekarang.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:46.63,0:13:48.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,Serahkan pertahanan kepadaku.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:48.39,0:13:50.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya. Ayo!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:00.01,0:14:02.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau berhasil mengenainya.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:06.98,0:14:07.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak mungkin!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:19.83,0:14:21.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa-apaan ia ini?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:24.17,0:14:26.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jika terus begini, kita akan kehabisan tenaga.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:33.18,0:14:37.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Serangan kita mempan, tapi kemampuan\Npemulihannya menghapus semua luka.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:37.91,0:14:39.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada bermacam-macam makhluk hidup.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:41.05,0:14:44.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dunia ini sungguh menarik.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:45.38,0:14:47.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku akan mencobanya.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:47.01,0:14:48.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ayo kita ganti formasi.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:54.45,0:14:56.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lucas, serangan bantuan!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:57.69,0:14:59.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku mengerti.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:02.92,0:15:07.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,Siapa yang akan melindungiku\Njika serangannya mengarah padaku?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:09.76,0:15:11.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa ini akan baik-baik saja?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:11.32,0:15:11.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:12.05,0:15:13.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mungkin.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:13.13,0:15:14.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mungkin katamu?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:14.58,0:15:16.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak ada cara lain.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:16.91,0:15:17.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku mengerti.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:20.06,0:15:21.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa, Lucas?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:21.81,0:15:25.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa kau benar-benar penyihir terbaik\Ndi Kerajaan Sapin?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:25.04,0:15:27.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan meremehkanku!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:35.85,0:15:38.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku adalah Lucas Wykes!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:49.58,0:15:51.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sesuai rencana, Elijah.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:52.09,0:15:52.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:58.47,0:15:59.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Elijah!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:08.45,0:16:09.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pemulihan dirinya terhenti.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:09.99,0:16:11.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lanjutkan seperti ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:11.74,0:16:12.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:30.21,0:16:31.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hore!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:33.75,0:16:35.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita berhasil mengalahkannya\Nberkat kau, Elijah.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:35.81,0:16:38.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku hanya melakukannya\Nsesuai perintahmu, Note.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:38.55,0:16:42.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dengan ini, nama keluarga Wykes\Nakan terangkat lagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:43.05,0:16:44.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lagi-lagi bicara seperti itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:46.01,0:16:50.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mereka yang memiliki kekuatan memikul\Ntanggung jawab dan tekanan yang besar.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:50.75,0:16:54.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Alasan aku tidak bisa mengabaikan\Nbangsawan muda ini,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:54.58,0:16:57.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,mungkin karena dia mengingatkanku\Npada diriku yang dulu.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:58.12,0:16:58.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:59.01,0:17:00.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:00.35,0:17:02.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tadi adalah api yang hebat.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:02.51,0:17:03.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tentu saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:09.55,0:17:11.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ia masih...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:12.61,0:17:14.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,Staminaku tinggal sedikit.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:14.17,0:17:16.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sampai sejauh mana aku bisa bertahan?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:28.01,0:17:30.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ketemu, Arthur.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:36.95,0:17:39.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sial! Menjauh! Menjauh!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:52.71,0:17:53.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa kau baik-baik saja?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:53.85,0:17:55.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa kau juga baik-baik saja, Jasmine?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:59.31,0:18:00.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:05.98,0:18:07.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi, ini
Dialogue: 10,0:18:07.21,0:18:09.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,kekuatan seorang petualang Kelas AA.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:09.95,0:18:12.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau boleh juga.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:15.58,0:18:19.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maaf, ini karena aku\Ntidak mencari tahu dengan benar.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:19.25,0:18:21.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku juga sama.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:21.25,0:18:22.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:22.35,0:18:24.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita ini satu party.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:24.81,0:18:26.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:26.11,0:18:27.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Arthur.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:27.85,0:18:30.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terima kasih sudah menolongku.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:33.98,0:18:36.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya, karena kita satu party.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:38.95,0:18:40.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Note!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:40.78,0:18:42.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tangkap ia!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:42.91,0:18:45.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mana Core yang sudah kita dapatkan!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:46.05,0:18:47.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku lupa.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:02.97,0:19:03.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,Serius?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:04.11,0:19:08.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hei, Tessia, kau belum bertemu dengan Arthur?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:08.35,0:19:12.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,Habisnya waktunya tidak pas terus.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:12.61,0:19:14.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Berarti itu, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:14.31,0:19:16.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Berarti itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:16.41,0:19:18.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau merasa takut, bukan?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:18.55,0:19:21.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hah? Tidak seperti itu!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:21.80,0:19:22.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baiklah.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:22.93,0:19:25.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku akan pergi sekarang.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:25.18,0:19:26.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lihat saja nanti.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:26.31,0:19:27.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tessia!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:28.45,0:19:29.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:29.61,0:19:31.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bayar dulu sebelum pergi.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:53.91,0:19:54.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku pasti bisa.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:55.65,0:19:59.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Karena aku adalah\Nputri dari Kerajaan Elenoir.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:59.71,0:20:02.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bertemu dengan teman lama itu\Nsesuatu yang mudah.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:03.35,0:20:04.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ayo, Tessia.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:12.15,0:20:13.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada perlu apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:16.29,0:20:19.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,Permisi.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:21.11,0:20:21.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa yang barusan
Dialogue: 10,0:20:23.18,0:20:24.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,adalah elf?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:26.45,0:20:30.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Xyrus pun sudah menjadi tempat di mana\Nkita bisa bertemu dengan ras lain.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:31.31,0:20:34.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sepertinya aliansi tiga negara\Nberjalan dengan baik.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:34.81,0:20:36.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Syukurlah.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:54.11,0:20:56.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sepertinya berjalan dengan lancar.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:56.18,0:20:57.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:57.38,0:20:59.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia bekerja dengan baik.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:00.18,0:21:02.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi masih belum cukup.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:09.08,0:21:13.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku harus mencari yang lebih kuat...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:16.53,0:21:18.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,untuk hari yang pasti akan datang.
